data.description: Welcome Home to Modern Comfort and Privacy in Branson, West, Missouri! This stunning 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom beauty offers a spacious 3352 sq. ft. of living space, including a finished walkout basement - the perfect family retreat! Nestled on 1.2 acres, enjoy your private oasis just minutes away from the world-renowned Silver Dollar City amusement park and a short stroll to Table Rock Lake. Step inside to discover beautiful bamboo flooring, a sprawling open-concept layout, and generously sized bedrooms with ample closet space. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting brand-new stainless steel appliances. Modern refrigerator (only 4 years old, included in the sale)  What's New in the home? Freshly installed front door and deck door, High-efficiency heat pump, Three-year-old HVAC system. All Updated kitchen appliances, Brand-new garbage disposal (Dec 2022) New hot water heater (2022) Stylish new faucet, Fresh new dishwasher (2021) New roof (2017) Replaced garage door springs (2021) New grinder pump for sewer system installed (2023) with a 3-year warranty, Recently remodeled and expanded deck, Brand-new water softener (owned by sellers) Lifetime warranty on bamboo flooring in dining and formal living rooms, Tile and laminate flooring throughout, Wet bar in the basement, Cozy propane fireplace upstairs and in the basement, Negotiable washer and dryer, Newly paved road (2 years ago) Gas stove, but the option for electric is available, Remodeled family room (2022), HVAC system only 3 years old, Abundant storage space beneath the lower deck and in the crawlspace. Community Amenities: Enjoy access to the clubhouse, outdoor swimming pool, tennis courts, and a basketball court. Boating enthusiasts will appreciate the convenient boat slips - perfect for a day on the water. This property seamlessly combines comfort, privacy, and entertainment, making it your ideal family home. Don't miss your chance to call it yours!
